Robert Middlemass https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Middlemass 0 Robert Middlemass (3 September 1883, New Britain, Connecticut – 10 September 1949, Los Angeles, California) was an American playwright and stage actor, and later character actor with over 100 film appearances. usually playing detectives or policemen.
